  <brief_title>Intracoronary Injection of Autologous Bone Marrow Cells in Patients With Chronic Heart Failure: Five Years Follow up</brief_title>
  <official_title>Intracoronary Injection of Autologous Bone Marrow Cells in Patients With Chronic Heart Failure: Five Years Follow up</official_title>
  <sponsors>
